name: Dockingstation
description: Big docking station. All metal walls except for the bay doors that is a transparent electric shield. You can see right into space.

name: Hallway
description: A long uninteressing corridor that connects locations in this spacestation in a secure manner.

name: Controlroom
description: Very large room. One big entrance. From the entrance you can see a 2 rows of desks on each side of the pathway that leads up to the main viewer. Almost looks like a theather.
